01:02:39.000 --> 01:02:43.190 align:middle line:10%
>> Well, you know
that fundamentally,

01:02:43.190 --> 01:02:46.670 align:middle line:10%
African music is
the rhythmic music.

01:02:46.670 --> 01:02:50.220 align:middle line:84%
It's polyrhythmic, whereas
European music we always speak

01:02:50.220 --> 01:02:52.470 align:middle line:90%
of as polyphonic music.

01:02:52.470 --> 01:02:54.560 align:middle line:84%
