01:04:19.790 --> 01:04:21.820 align:middle line:90%
of the phrase.

01:04:21.820 --> 01:04:24.290 align:middle line:84%
Well, that rhythm
we know travels

01:04:24.290 --> 01:04:28.050 align:middle line:84%
through many, many
different variations,

01:04:28.050 --> 01:04:32.120 align:middle line:84%
Bizet's "Habanera" from
"Carmen" is one variation of it,

01:04:32.120 --> 01:04:36.460 align:middle line:84%
