01:07:13.180 --> 01:07:18.670 align:middle line:84%
>> I was actually interested
in how Native American practice

01:07:18.670 --> 01:07:21.730 align:middle line:84%
merged with African
spirituality.

01:07:21.730 --> 01:07:27.730 align:middle line:84%
That's been a repeating
theme in many of the people

01:07:27.730 --> 01:07:32.070 align:middle line:90%
