01:07:32.070 --> 01:07:36.940 align:middle line:10%
>> Well, here's the
story, as it come to me.

01:07:36.940 --> 01:07:40.600 align:middle line:10%
When they moved the slaves here,
when they moved the Africans,

01:07:40.600 --> 01:07:44.230 align:middle line:10%
their gods became like them.

01:07:44.230 --> 01:07:46.540 align:middle line:84%
Powerful gods like
Legba would suddenly

01:07:46.540 --> 01:07:52.850 align:middle line:84%
