drunkard, living in rags.

01:07:52.850 --> 01:07:57.520 align:middle line:84%
What happened is that
when they came here,

01:07:57.520 --> 01:08:00.970 align:middle line:84%
two peoples had very
similar understanding

01:08:00.970 --> 01:08:03.220 align:middle line:84%
of the Earth, the
relationship with the planet,

01:08:03.220 --> 01:08:05.830 align:middle line:84%
the relationship with
trees, everything.

01:08:05.830 --> 01:08:09.910 align:middle line:84%
And they were both being
oppressed by the same guy.

01:08:09.910 --> 01:08:11.920 align:middle line:90%
So they came together.

01:08:11.920 --> 01:08:14.810 align:middle line:84%
And they did this in the
hills and mountains of Haiti.

01:08:14.810 --> 01:08:18.056 align:middle line:84%
The natives there that
Columbus hadn't killed

01:08:18.056 --> 01:08:19.930 align:middle line:90%
had run off to the mountains.

01:08:19.930 --> 01:08:23.590 align:middle line:84%
And so the Africans,
to do their religion,

01:08:23.590 --> 01:08:25.839 align:middle line:84%
because you know it
was devil worship

01:08:25.839 --> 01:08:27.880 align:middle line:84%
according to the Catholics
that were around them,

01:08:27.880 --> 01:08:29.979 align:middle line:84%
they had to go off
into the woods.

01:08:29.979 --> 01:08:32.080 align:middle line:84%
And when they was
in the woods, they

01:08:32.080 --> 01:08:34.029 align:middle line:90%
run into the Native Americans.

01:08:34.029 --> 01:08:35.080 align:middle line:90%
And they got together.

01:08:35.080 --> 01:08:36.700 align:middle line:90%
They began to powwow.

01:08:36.700 --> 01:08:40.310 align:middle line:84%
Powwow really meant
healing ceremony.

01:08:40.310 --> 01:08:42.130 align:middle line:90%
That's what powwow means.

01:08:42.130 --> 01:08:44.590 align:middle line:90%
And they came together.

01:08:44.590 --> 01:08:50.470 align:middle line:84%
And from this merging, all
the petra, the fire ceremonies

01:08:50.470 --> 01:08:53.890 align:middle line:84%
and Voodoo in New
Orleans, Haitian Voodoo

01:08:53.890 --> 01:08:58.029 align:middle line:84%
came about through this blend,
which is where the Mardi Gras

01:08:58.029 --> 01:09:00.439 align:middle line:90%
Indian tradition comes from.

01:09:00.439 --> 01:09:06.700 align:middle line:84%
And I think it's very telling
that the Mardi Gras Indians use

01:09:06.700 --> 01:09:10.149 align:middle line:84%
the Indian, because they had
to have somebody who was going

01:09:10.149 --> 01:09:12.049 align:middle line:90%
to fight the gods of Europe.

01:09:12.049 --> 01:09:13.840 align:middle line:84%
And so they started
talking to the Indians.

01:09:13.840 --> 01:09:15.965 align:middle line:84%
And the Indians fell in
love with the black people.

01:09:15.965 --> 01:09:19.660 align:middle line:84%
Oh, you are pretty, a
totally different view.

01:09:19.660 --> 01:09:23.020 align:middle line:84%
White folks, well, they're ugly,
stupid, they look like monkey.

01:09:23.020 --> 01:09:25.029 align:middle line:84%
And to the Indians,
it's like, oh,

01:09:25.029 --> 01:09:30.430 align:middle line:90%
beautiful, fearless, powerful.

01:09:30.430 --> 01:09:34.060 align:middle line:84%
There was no problem falling
in love, none at all.

01:09:34.060 --> 01:09:37.060 align:middle line:84%
And the thing that they had to
consider-- because the Indians

01:09:37.060 --> 01:09:39.370 align:middle line:90%
