slave, nor were their children.

01:09:46.540 --> 01:09:49.450 align:middle line:84%
They wouldn't live
on your plantation.

01:09:49.450 --> 01:09:51.310 align:middle line:90%
And they would help the husband.

01:09:51.310 --> 01:09:53.200 align:middle line:84%
But they would have
their own garden.

01:09:53.200 --> 01:09:58.150 align:middle line:84%
And they would eventually
buy their husband's freedom.

01:09:58.150 --> 01:10:00.100 align:middle line:84%
And this is where you
get the whole thing

01:10:00.100 --> 01:10:02.890 align:middle line:90%
of free people of color.

01:10:02.890 --> 01:10:04.840 align:middle line:84%
That's one of the big
New Orleans things.

01:10:04.840 --> 01:10:07.547 align:middle line:84%
It's one of the few
places in the South

01:10:07.547 --> 01:10:09.130 align:middle line:84%
